						<summary>

						<p>A pillar of the same <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription is in Tamil verse.</p>						

						<p>It records that a certain woman named Uyyavandāḷ of Kōdaykuḍi caused a <hi rend="italic">maṇi-maṇḍapa</hi> to be built (in the temple) of Tambirāṉār, (which was) a gift of Danti, by the grace (of the Tambirāṉ). </p>						

						</summary>
